{"tid":1851860,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果真係無晒正版口罩，用住made in china既救救口罩得唔得?","createTime":"2020-01-30T07:50:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T09:00:09.000Z","uid":172077,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c34b360fb26bf6690dabd33e14b7e8b790e33a4b","tid":1851860,"uid":172077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T07:50:24.000Z","msg":"我得番一盒救救口罩，<br />\n係有少少薄，但未去到好透個隻，同埋正常氣味，都接受到，頂住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但其實救救口罩係咪都有分高仿同低仿，<br />\n上網見到人地d救救口罩勁薄，係薄到透個隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者同一時間戴兩個救救口罩，會唔會安全d?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"250bdf026fa197f8f9bcaf8d021c809facddd0c2","tid":1851860,"uid":336645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T07:53:19.000Z","msg":"聽聞二手重用"},{"pid":"5ea095ecdadba50d2217e688cb25f4456249addf","tid":1851860,"uid":172077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"250bdf026fa197f8f9bcaf8d021c809facddd0c2","tid":1851860,"uid":336645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T07:53:19.000Z","msg":"聽聞二手重用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T07:54:26.000Z","msg":"但望落都無咩唔正常，無咩漬"},{"pid":"a8f49cb7b3cfa941b7bedb0c8d5b729e05253fa9","tid":1851860,"uid":6033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T07:57:06.000Z","msg":"唔出街最實際"},{"pid":"b22aaf4b1fb09607a6b378773816b618915801f1","tid":1851860,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T08:00:51.000Z","msg":"唔好出街，如果要反工要要你老闆提供口罩，如果佢唔提供，就寫一封話如果因無口罩而感染到就要佢負全責，要佢簽名加公司蓋章"},{"pid":"2d08a5dc8b5ff3bcb69a913dc505c24f86a6135f","tid":1851860,"uid":267403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T08:00:56.000Z","msg":"寧可死在重用中，不用支那黑貨亡"},{"pid":"23b08bea234ae07e5a8edf12d98922b85dece468","tid":1851860,"uid":200389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"250bdf026fa197f8f9bcaf8d021c809facddd0c2"